2070. Casey Jones and Iris Owen investigate the murder of the director of the Friedrich Corps, a company specializing in cybernetics.

Their journey will lead them on the trail of a cyborg decided to get rid of any human trace. A hunt to the depths of the planet, in a place called CHROME!
